@GovKemp Mr Governor my question is...since...
Covid-19 is contagious two DAYS prior to Temperature
and symptoms .... How will I know if I am safe to eat out.
Are you comfortable w/ your mother eating out?
***iF Death rate increases will you resign as Governor? ***
